Author: grewalsatinder#9653
Content:
this teaches a lesson actually. which I guess many won't understand.
If you buy a cryptocurrency token on very cheap, it doesn't mean you'll be millionaire in future for sure, even if that cryptocurrency goes multiple times the value gradually. the bear markets in between are brutal and you can lose the investment to survive in between.
The ones who plan and build some fundamental rules to keep the financials sorted might survive and will do become millionaire gradually if they keep maintaining their position on their original investment.

Author: cipi#4502
Content:
on stock markets, there is a good way of predicting prices of stocks by analyzing the data from CBOE of the issued calls/puts for the stocks
the price on the day these calls/puts expire will be the price that is best for the issuer of these calls/puts (max. profit, min. losses)
that is likely what hapenned to BTC too in the last days
